  "text": "In our opinion a main development for the \"Città Ideale\" app is to carry out experimental user tests, which examine the engagement and emotional response of visitors. We expect that the Urbino's Ducal Palace will participate to the debate recently engaged among international museum critics, curators, and neuroscientists [CITATION_1] .",
